------ PROJECT-BAR DEVELOPMENT ------

Please follow this configuration to develop Project-BAR.
If you think there is a better alternative, please send an e-mail to hugo.duprat@gmail.com with the tag [project-bar].

Qt Creator version:  2.6.2
Qt version: 5.0.1
libsox version: 14.4.1
MinGW version: 4.7 32bit
Doxygen version: 1.8.3.1

To use Qt 5.0.1 with MinGW 4.7, you have to add a new kit in QtCreator (Tools > Options > Build & Run > Kits, then Add. Change the compiler to MinGW 4.7 32bit (normally auto-detected).
